Packages that use AeActivityDef
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def This package contains base classes and elements used to create BPEL model definitions. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.activity This package contains classes which define the various BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io This package contains the BPEL reader and writer interfaces and the factory classes to access them. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.readers.def This package contains the IAeBpelDefReader interface for reading in BPEL xml and the default impls. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.io.writers.def This package contains the IAeBpelDefWriter interface for serializing specific AeBaseDef object subclasses and the default impls. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.util Utilities for handling expressions, variable properties, and package data.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation This package contains classes which support BPEL validation.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors Classes implementing the Visitor pattern used to perform various functions on the activity definitions.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity This package contains classes used in the implementation model for the BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web.processview This package contains all the code and presentation beans for driving the web app Process Details view ui.
